dct_title_s: Map showing streets and lots from 27th Street to 36th Street
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from 27th Street to 36th Street along the Delaware River. Map depicts the various properties and owners in Camden City along the Delaware River. Map also shows high and low water lines.
